      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>I knew pretty much right away that I wanted the truck to be the main character of the piece.  Having already had most of this model in an older form as an ice cream truck, I set about turning it into a UFO-hunting van.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"icecreamtruck.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/icecreamtruck.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755699261375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=408\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/563118083/icecreamtruck.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755699261375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1101\" data-width=\"2047\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"563183654\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"icecreamtruck.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"563118083\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"13\" data-media-id=\"90cd6870-2fd8-4771-ba8f-c14747abb753\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/icecreamtruck.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755699261375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=816 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/icecreamtruck.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755699261375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=408 1x\"></span><p>In the real world, you often see re-purposed vehicles.  A van that once drove around town serving ice cream was up for sale and purchased by a UFO hunter, who converted it for another use.  The more I thought about the backstory, the more the character developed.</p><p>The first step was to add some extra geometry to the van to show that it had been customized and equipped with a UFO-hunting kit.  Radar dishes, CCTV cameras, bigger off-road wheels, a bull bar, and a roof rack full of tracking equipment.  </p><p>Once the outside was done, I then concentrated on the inside.  As I progressed with some initial renders, I realised I wanted to add some monitors and ‘light’ to the inside of the truck, so I added desks and monitors.  </p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><a href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/563118083/TRUCK.mov?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755698420262&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760\">TRUCK.mov</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"TheHunted_van_1.png\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/TheHunted_van_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755698534769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/563118083/TheHunted_van_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755698534769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"563478553\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"TheHunted_van_1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"563118083\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"13\" data-media-id=\"59c9652a-6059-4e84-bf62-c1bb0c6cc042\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/TheHunted_van_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755698534769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/TheHunted_van_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755698534769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=200 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"TheHunted_van_2.png\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/TheHunted_van_2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755698546758&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/563118083/TheHunted_van_2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755698546758&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"563150855\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"TheHunted_van_2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"563118083\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"13\" data-media-id=\"ffa5ff3c-e6d9-467e-b27d-a176b936a4b3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/563118083/TheHunted_van_2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=17